Gem & Genie Bulk Sniper is a powerful NFT automation tool designed for fast and efficient NFT trading on the Gem and Genie aggregators. This advanced NFT sniper automatically monitors the market and instantly purchases NFTs that meet your predefined criteria, including price range, specific collections, rarity, traits, and floor conditions.

Built for professional NFT traders and collectors, Gem & Genie Bulk Sniper helps users gain a competitive edge in high-demand NFT markets by eliminating manual searches and reducing reaction time to near zero. The tool supports bulk buying, allowing users to acquire multiple NFTs in a single workflow, optimize gas efficiency, and capitalize on undervalued assets before others can react.
